text: Varzesh3 (Persian: ورزش سه, varzeš seh, "Sport 3") is an Iranian website that primarily covers association football, as well as other Sports. The website is owned by Farakav group. According to Alexa, as of July 2020, Varzesh3 is the 382th most popular website in the world. == References == Category:Association football websites Category:Persian-language websites
title: Varzesh3
